<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Loggin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../cssgeneral/bootstrap.min.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../cssalumnos/index.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="formulario">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col col-6">
                <p><a id="new" class="btn btn-secondary m-4" href="/alumnos">Ir ala vista Alumnos.</a></p>
                <p class="m-4">Da clic en el enlace de arriba para ir ala vista alumnos y realizar modificaciones
                    ala BD.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col col-6">
                 <div id="flex">
                    <h3 class="text-center">Inicia sesion</h3>
                    <form action="/session/iniciar" method="post">
                        <label for="inputUser">Usuario</label>
                        <input type="text"     class="forms-control" name="tfUsuario" id="inputUser" placeholder="Usuario">
                        <label for="inputPass">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" class="forms-control" name="tfPassword" id="inputPass" placeholder="Password">

                        <button type="submit" value="IniciarSesion" class="btn-Sesion">Loggin</button>
                    </form>

                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
     </div>
</body>
</html>